Edged....and just short! Well bowled! On a length, outside off, shaping away. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to block this, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards Sarel Erwee who collects it on the bounce.
Another length delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out towards cover.
Tad fuller, angling in around middle and leg, at 134 clicks. Najmul Hossain Shanto taps it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller in length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods forward and defends it out.
Angling in, around middle, at 132 clicks. Tamim Iqbal blocks it out watchfully.
Pitches it up, around middle and leg. Tamim Iqbal pushes it towards mid on.
On a length, outside off. Tamim Iqbal hangs back and blocks it out.
Duanne Olivier drops it short now, around middle. Tamim Iqbal ducks under it.
Swinging in, fuller ball, around middle, at 128 clicks. Tamim Iqbal closes the face of his bat and taps it towards square leg.
Full again, around middle. Tamim Iqbal pushes it with the inner half of his bat towards mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it on the off side.
Angling in, around middle, shorter ball. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it out.
Outside off, on a length. Najmul Hossain Shanto lets that go through to the keeper.
Swinging in, outside off, touch fuller. Najmul Hossain Shanto strides forward and defends it solidly.
Pitches it up again, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives but the ball goes off the inner half of his bat back to the bowler.
Fuller again, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto pushes it wide of mid on and scampers through to the other end.
On a length, around off, at 130 clicks. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out off the front foot.
On a length, tailing back in, around the thigh pads. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on the thigh pad.
Nipping back in, outside off, on a length. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
Duanne Olivier drops it short now, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto ducks underneath it.
Fuller ball, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans to block this but the ball goes off the inside edge back onto his pads.
Beaten! Outside off, on a length. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to have a poke at it but he misses.
Simon Harmer begins with a shorter ball, outside off. Tamim Iqbal blocks it out off the back foot.
FOUR! Cut away! Another shorter delivery, spinning away, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hangs back and slashes it past point for a boundary.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it out.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto pushes it to the fielder at cover.
Tosses it up, full in length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans to drive this, but the ball goes off the outside edge away from first slip. Two taken!
Fuller length delivery, around middle and off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it out.
A length ball, on middle. Iqbal turns it to mid-wicket where a misfield allows a single.
Length ball, outside off. Shanto shuffles across and blocks it to covers.
Full ball from around the wicket and around off. Shanto gets a straight bat down to defend it.
Short and tailing down the leg side. Shanto misses his pull.
Full ball, outside off. Shanto gets on the front foot to defend it.
On a length and on middle. Blocked out.
Tossed up, angling on middle. Iqbal leans and defends it.
Fuller and slanting on middle. Iqbal looks to defend on the front foot but gets an outside edge to third man and couple of runs are taken.
Tossed up, on middle. Iqbal skips down and lofts it to deep cover for a single.
On middle. Blocked to mid-wicket.
This one lands on off and turns away. Shanto pads it away.
Loopy ball, on off. Shanto gets low to block it.
FOUR! Welcomes Williams with a boundary! A length ball, angling on middle. Iqbal steps across and flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Slants it on middle. Tamim defends it out.
FOUR! Iqbal is dealing in boundaries! Overpitched and on middle. Iqbal drives it beautifully past mid on for a boundary.
Length and on off. Defended on the front foot.
Short of a length and on off. Tamim defends with a straight bat.
A length ball, angling around middle and leg. Iqbal looks to flick but misses and gets hit on the pads. An appeal for LBW but that was sliding down.
Tossed up, full and on middle, it turns away sharply. Shanto leans to defend but misses.

A touch short and outside off, turning away. Shanto misses his cut. The keeper dislodges the bails but the replay shows nothing on UltraEdge while Shanto's back foot was hanging in the air. The stump camera gives a good angle for the third umpire but still the third umpire thinks there is no conclusive evidence and the big screen shows Not out.
Shorter and outside off, hit to mid on.
Tossed up, on off. Shanto prods to defend.
Nicely floated, on middle. Shanto keeps it out as he reaches to the ball.
Too full and on middle. Shanto bunts it to square leg for a single.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Outside off again. Shanto offers no shot.
Length ball, tailing around off. Shanto defends it towards extra cover.
FOUR! Pitches it up and outside off. Shanto muscles it past the bowler and to long off for a boundary. Dealing in boundaries.
Touch short and outside off. Shanto punches it to covers.
Fuller and outside off. Shanto knocks it to covers.
FOUR! Nicely done! Fuller delivery, around middle. Tamim Iqbal gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Tamim Iqbal pushes it past the second slip fielder. Temba Bavuma chases the ball and keeps it down to two runs.
Back of a length outside off. Tamim Iqbal cuts it towards point.
Tosses it up, full, around his pads. Tamim Iqbal leans and defends it out.
Loopy delivery, around middle, fuller ball. Tamim Iqbal defends it out.
FOUR BYES! Firing it down the leg side, fuller ball. Tamim Iqbal misses his flick, the keeper fails to collect the ball as well. The ball races away towards the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Fuller delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
Another pitched up delivery, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto has defended this solidly off the front foot.
Fuller delivery, outside off at 139 clicks. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans and drives it to the fielder at mid off.
Lizaad Williams pulls his length back now, outside off, at 135 clicks. Najmul Hossain Shanto taps it towards cover-point off the back foot.
Fullish delivery, angling in, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out.
Shorter delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto presents the full face of the bat and defends it out.
Well bowled! Sharp turn there for Simon Harmer! A loopy delivery, full, outside off, spinning away. Tamim Iqbal leans to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg, quicker and flatter as well. Taijul Islam works it away past square leg for a single.
FOUR! Top shot! Another fuller delivery, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets down on his knee and sweeps it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
Beaten! Tosses it up, fuller ball, outside off spinning away. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods to block this but he misses.
FOUR! Another boundary in the over! Down leg this time, fuller ball. Najmul Hossain Shanto paddle-sweeps it towards fine leg for a boundary.
Loopy delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
Angling in, around off, on a length. Tamim Iqbal blocks it out.
Pitches it up again, around middle and off. Tamim Iqbal pushes it towards the fielder at mid on.
Fuller in length, outside off. Tamim Iqbal defends it out off the front foot.
Another length delivery, outside off. Tamim Iqbal defends it out solidly.
Fuller delivery, angling in, around middle. Tamim Iqbal drags it towards mid on through the inner half of his bat.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Tamim Iqbal tucks it past square leg for single.
Keshav Maharaj begins with a fuller ball, turning in, around middle. Tamim Iqbal leans to drive but the ball goes off the inner half of the bat towards long on for a single.
Loopy delivery, fuller in length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and defends it out.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto sweeps it towards square leg. No run there!
Pitches it up, loopy delivery, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans to block this but the ball goes off the inside edge towards square leg for a single.

FOUR! Lucky boundary! A fuller ball, quicker this time, down the leg side. Tamim Iqbal looks to reverse-sweep this but the ball goes off the top edge and over the keeper's head, towards the fine leg fence for a boundary.

An appeal for LBW, but not given! A fuller delivery, around middle. Tamim Iqbal gets down on his knee and tries to sweep this but he misses. The replay shows that the ball goes off the gloves towards point. Single taken!
A length ball, outside off, shaping in late. Iqbal shoulders arms to it.
Short of a length, outside off. Iqbal gets on top to cut it but gets a bottom edge, onto his pads.
Outside off. Left alone.
No run.

OUT! LBW! A length ball, just outside off, again it nips back in sharply. Iqbal looks to defend but gets beaten on the inside edge and gets hit on the pads. An appeal for LBW and up goes the finger. Iqbal was not quite sure and he walks across to his partner but after a small conversation, he makes the long walk back to the hut.
Howout: lbw b Wiaan Mulder

Commentary: Short in length and angling outside off. Haque shoulders arms to it.
Darted on the pads, flicked to square leg for a single.
Flatter and spinning around off. Haque blocks it.
Tossed up, on middle. Haque whips it to deep square leg and gets across with a single.
Around off. Shanto tucks it to square leg.
Loopy ball, on off, eased down to long on for a single.
Fuller and on off. Haque defends on the front foot to covers. A slight mix-up in between but no harm done.
A length ball, outside off. Shanto blocks it on the off side.
Length ball, way outside off. left alone.
Another leave as that was outside off.
On middle. Blocked out.

OUT! LBW! This is full and comes with the angle from round the wicket, on off. Shanto tries to flick it across but misses and gets rapped on the front pad. An appeal for LBW but nothing given. Mulder was convinced and asks his captain to take it upstairs. UltraEdge shows no bat and Ball Tracking shows three reds. Wonderful review from South Africa.
Howout: lbw b Wiaan Mulder

Commentary: Length and on middle. Blocked out.
Fuller and on off. Haque prods and dead bats it.
NoAngles it on middle. Haque keeps it out on the leg side.
Flatter and outside off. Haque knocks it to covers.

Did that carry? Tossed up, around off. Haque leans and looks to defend but this one comes straight and takes the outside edge to first slip where Keegan Petersen is on his heels and tries to take it low to his left but fails to do so. Was really hard but will count as a dropped catch.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
A loopy ball and it is blocked out.
FOUR! A length ball, outside off. Rahim looks to defend with soft hands and it goes off the splice and through the gully region for a boundary.
Full and angling on middle, from over the wicket. Rahim dead bats it.
Length ball, slanting on off and holds its line. Rahim blocks it solidly.
On middle. Rahim defends under his eyes.
Length ball, drifting on off. Rahim looks to defend but gets an outside edge to third slip who catches it on a bounce.
Carbon copy of the previous delivery. Rahim is getting away as he is defending with soft hands.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mominul Haque pushes it back to the bowler.
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Mominul Haque drives it towards mid on.
Pitches it up, around middle. Mominul Haque leans and nudges it towards square leg.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to flick this on the leg side, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards the off side.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mominul Haque pushes it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Down the leg side, fuller ball. Mominul Haque gets down on his knee and sweeps it past square leg for a boundary.
Angling in, fuller ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim drives it towards mid on.
On a length, outside off, shaping away. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
On a length, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it to mid-wicket.
Marginally short, around middle and off. Mushfiqur Rahim shows the full face of his bat and defends it out.
Shorter ball again, around middle and off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Angling in, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it past square leg for a single. He retains the strike!
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back and pushes it towards cover for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mominul Haque leans and blocks it out solidly.
Loopy delivery, full in length, on the pads. Mominul Haque looks to flick this, but the ball goes off the inside edge onto the pads and lobs up away from the short leg fielder. Single taken!
FOUR! Swept away! Fuller delivery, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and sweeps it past square leg for a boundary.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim works it away towards mid on.
Flighted delivery, outside off, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim presses forward and blocks it out.
Angling in, on a length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Fuller delivery, swinging in, around middle, at 129 clicks. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Good-length delivery, angling in, around middle and leg. Mominul Haque tucks it towards square leg.
Nipping back in, outside off, on a length. Mominul Haque does not fiddle with it.
Another one tailing in, around middle. Mominul Haque leans to block this but the ball goes off the inside edge towards square leg.

OUT! LBW! Wiaan Mulder strikes yet again! He has got all three batters in a similar way! A length delivery, nipping back in, around middle. Mominul Haque leans to block this but he misses and gets rapped on his front pad. A huge appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger. Mominul Haque consults his partner but he does not take the review. Mominul Haque departs. It's the inswinging delivery of Wiaan Mulder causing all sorts of trouble.
Howout: lbw b Wiaan Mulder

Commentary: FOUR! Streaky! A shorter ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back, waits for it, and cuts it late, towards third man for a boundary.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards cover.
Another loopy delivery, fuller ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim presses forward and blocks it out.
Slower through the air, full, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim opens the face of his bat and pushes it past point for a single.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around middle. Liton Das leans and defends it out.
Outside off, spinning away, fuller ball. Liton Das pushes it towards backward point. The fielder there runs across, dives over the ball and the batters take a single!
A length ball, outside off. Das guides it through cover-point for a couple of runs.
FOUR! A length ball, outside off. Das leans a bit and pushes it nicely past covers for a boundary.
On a length and on off. Defended out.
A length ball, angling outside off. Das taps it to covers.
FOUR! Another superb shot! Short of a length, outside off. Das punches through covers for a boundary.
Short of a length, this one nips away. Das looks to defend on the up but misses.

Floated and on middle. Rahim looks to sweep but misses and gets hit on the body. The ball lobs and goes to first slip who takes a good catch. Now, not quite sure what South Africa are appealing for but they were confident. A huge appeal but nothing given. They take the review. UltraEdge shows no bat while Ball Tracking shows wickets missing.
length and on off. Rahim guides it to third man for a couple of runs.
A quicker one, on middle. Rahim hangs on the back foot to defend.
Tossed up, on off. Rahim leans and blocks it.
FOUR! Releases some pressure! Tossed up, full and on off. Rahim sweeps it, aerially and to mid-wicket for a boundary.
Angles a full ball, on middle. Rahim keeps it out.
A full ball, around off, it nips away a bit. Das looks to defend but slices it to gully.
Down the leg side. Das leaves it alone.
Length and on middle. Das sees it out.
Length ball, swinging around off. Das prods and knocks it to covers.
Too full and outside off, pushed to covers.

OUT! BOWLED 'EM! Through the gates! What a delivery! A length ball, angling on middle and it nips back. Das looks to work on the leg side but misses and the ball goes through the gates and scatters the stumps. Bangladesh in a bit of trouble here.
Howout: b Duanne Olivier

Commentary: Tossed up, full and on off. Rahim takes a big stride forward to defend but it takes the outside edge and lobs over silly point.
Length and on middle. Blocked out.
On middle, swept to long leg for a couple of runs.
This one lands on off and spins away. Rahim is drawn to defend on the back foot but misses.
Too full and on leg. Rahim digs it out back to Maharaj.
Flatter and angling outside off. Rahim covers his stumps and leaves it.
Targets a short ball, around off. Ali bends and lets it through.
Length ball, angling down the leg side. Ali misses his flick.
A length ball, outside off. Ali plays with soft hands to the slip cordon.
Around off, pushed to covers.
Angles it around off and makes it to move away after landing. Ali is squared as he looks to defend.
Short of a length, outside off. ALi gets on top of the bounce and taps it through the gully region for a brace.
Flatter and angling around off. Rahi looks to cut but this was too close to his body.

Tossed up, full and on off. Rahim looks to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads. An appeal follows but stifled one. South Africa still take the review and there is clearly bat there. Maharaj knew it!
On the pads, tucked to square leg for a single.
Maharaj is getting the turn but fails to induce the edge again! Around off, it lands and spins away. Ali misses his defensive shot.
And again! Ali is prod to play this out but the spin takes the ball away and past his outside edge.
Too full and on middle. Ali blocks it out.
Angling in, fuller ball, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim clips it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Shorter ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the back foot.
Nipping back in, shorter ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim sways away from it.
Width on offer this time, shorter ball. Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it towards the fielder at cover-point.
On a length, tailing back in, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick this but he gets an inside edge back onto the pads.
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Yasir Ali leans and blocks it out.
Fuller delivery, spinning away, outside off. Yasir Ali looks to defend this but he bails out at the end.
Tosses it up, around middle, fuller in length. Yasir Ali leans and blocks it out.
Shortish delivery, outside off, spinning away. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Beaten! Well bowled! A loopy delivery, outside off, spinning away. Yasir Ali leans and tries to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
FOUR! Shorter ball, outside off. Yasir Ali hangs back and punches it past cover for a boundary.

FOUR! In the air....and just over! A fuller ball, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and sweeps this, but the ball goes off the top edge over the fielder at short fine leg for a boundary.
Fuller ball, spinning in, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim stays back and gets an inside edge back onto his pads.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out off the front foot.
Full, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim steps down the pitch and pushes it back to the bowler.
Spinning in, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his pads. There was an appeal for LBW, but turned down!
Fuller delivery, around middle and off. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it past square leg for a single.
Shorter ball, arpund middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Outside off, slower through the air, fuller ball. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover.
Slower through the air, full, spinning away, around middle and off. Yasir Ali leans to block this but he misses, the ball hits his forehand and lobs hup towards first slip.
Fuller, around middle. Yasir Ali pushes it back to the bowler.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Yasir Ali cuts it towards point.
Shorter ball again, around middle and off. Yasir Ali looks to flick this on the leg side, but the ball goes off the outside edge away from the slip fielder. Two taken!
Turning in, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone, the ball hits his pads and lobs up towards leg slip.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it to cover.
Loopy delivery, full, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim steps down and flicks it to mid-wicket.
Flatter ball, quicker around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Slower through the air, full, around leg, spinning in. Mushfiqur Rahim steps down the pitch and looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his pads.
Shorter ball, spinning in, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone. The ball hits him on his pads and lobs up towards leg slip. That will be Stumps on Day 2!
FOUR! Boundary to start the Day! Short of a length, outside off. Ali hops and guides it through the gap, between second slip and gully for a boundary.
FOUR! Confident start! Short and way outside off. Ali drives it past point for a boundary.

FOUR! This is some intent from Ali! Three in a row! This is on a length and way outside off. Ali plays it late and to the left of point for another boundary. Superb start for Bangladesh! 150 up as well.
A length ball, on off. Ali prods and blocks it out.
A length ball, outside off, nipping back in. Ali steps across and dead bats it on the off side.
On middle, on a length, tucked to square leg for a single. 13 runs off the over. Bangladesh off to a flier on Day 3.
Length ball, angling around off and then making it shape away. Ali reads it well to keep it out.
Straight around off. Blocked out.
Full and outside off. Ali drives it hard and to covers for a certain boundary but Bavuma there puts his body on the line to stop the ball. He hurts himself in the process.
Bangs a bouncer, around off. Rahim evades it well.
Length ball, slanting on middle. Rahim blocks it on the leg side.
Outside off and shaping more away. Left alone.
FOUR! Ali is dealing in boundaries! This is just too easy for him! On a length and outside off. Ali opens the face of the bat and dabs it through point for a boundary.
Length and slanting around off. Ali gets his bat down and plays it on the deck.
Short of a length and outside off. Ali hits it to point.
Length and on off. Defended out.
Touch fuller and drifting around middle, flicked to square leg for a single.
Short and outside off. Rahim shoulders arms to it.
A length ball, outside off, hint of away swing. Ali offers no shot.
Length ball, swinging away from the batter. Yasir stands tall and blocks it on the surface.
FOUR! On the pads this time, Ali flicks is beautifully and with proper timing to square leg for a boundary.
Short in length and outside off. A back foot punch from Ali but straight to cover.
On middle. Blocked out.
Length ball, outside off. Ali punches this through covers and Bavuma does well to chase it and keep it down to a single.
On a length, nipping back in, outside off. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Another length delivery, angling in, around middle. Yasir Ali looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his thigh pad.
Tad fuller now, tailing back in, around middle. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Length delivery, around middle and leg. Yasir Ali looks to block this but the ball goes off the inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Leg bye! Darting it on the pads, length delivery. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to tuck this but he misses. The ball brushes off his pads and rolls towards square leg. Leg bye taken!
Fuller length delivery, around middle and leg. Yasir Ali pushes it with the inner half of his bat towards square leg and takes a single.
Pitches it up, outside off. Yasir Ali presses forward and blocks it out.
Much straighter this time, on the pads, fuller ball. Yasir Ali flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
A huge shout for LBW, but not given! A length ball, angling in, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick this but he gets an inside edge back onto his pads.
On a length, around the fourth stump line. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Duanne Olivier drops it short now, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim ducks under it and lets that go through.
FOUR! Top shot! Short again, width on offer. Mushfiqur Rahim stays in his crease and slashes it past point for a boundary.

WIDE! Too short on this occasion, around middle. Yasir Ali ducks and lest that go through. Kyle Verreynne behind the stumps, jumps high and does well to grab the ball. Wide called for height and that brings up the 50-run partnership between these two!
Fuller delivery, around middle and off. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Angling in on a length, around middle. Yasir Ali shows the full face of his bat and defends it out.
Outside off, on a length. Yasir Ali taps it towards point.
Pitches it up, around off. Yasir Ali presses forward and blocks it out solidly.
Shorter ball, down leg, at 132 clicks. Yasir Ali ducks and lets that go through.
Fuller delivery, angling in, around middle, at 136 clicks. Yasir Ali closes the face of his bat and tucks it to mid-wicket.
FOUR! Lovely shot! A fuller ball, shaping away, wide of off. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and drives it uppishly over point for a boundary.
Beaten! Well bowled! Fuller ball again, outside off, shaping away. Mushfiqur Rahim leans to drive but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
On a length, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Another length delivery, outside off, at 130 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim lets that go through to the keeper.
Shaping away, wide of off, length delivery. Mushfiqur Rahim shoulders his arms at it.
Length delivery, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim does not fiddle with it.
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Yasir Ali pushes it towards mid off.
Slower through the air, pitched up again, around middle. Yasir Ali defends it out solidly off the front foot.
Tosses it up again, full, around middle. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Fuller delivery, around the leg pole. Yasir Ali uses his wrist and flicks it past square leg for a boundary.
Flighted delivery, full, around middle. Yasir Ali presses forward and defends it out.
Spinning away, fuller ball, outside off. Yasir Ali blocks it front of the silly point fielder.
Leg bye! A length ball, tailing on the pads. Rahim misses his flick and gets hit on the pads. It rolls to square leg and a leg bye is taken.
Fuller and on off. Ali leans and defends it solidly.
Fuller ball, around middle. Ali defends across to mid-wicket.
Stumps to stumps from Wiaan Mulder and Ali is strong in his defense.
Length ball, on middle. Ali prods and defends close to the pad. He is oozing confidence right now.
Length and outside off. Defended to covers.
An arm ball, sliding on middle.Rahim lunges and blocks it out.
Tossed up, full and around off. Rahim defends on the front foot.
Keeps bowling it full and on middle. Rahim presses forward and keeps it out.

South Africa are celebrating but the umpire is unmoved. There was a noise and sharp turn as well. Tossed up, full and around off, it lands and spins away sharply. Rahim prods to defend but seems to miss it and gets beaten on the outside edge. First slip takes the catch and appeals but nothing given. South Africa have to be sure as they have only one review left. They don't take it.
A quicker one, on middle. Rahim rocks back and blocks it out.
Fuller and on middle. Rahim knocks it on the off side.
Fuller an on middle. Ali defends near his pads and gets an inside edge to mid-wicket.
length and on middle. Blocked out by Ali.
Overpitched and outside off, driven through covers for a single.
Angles it around off and it nips away a touch. Rahim leans to defend it.
On a length and around off. Rahim guides it to point.
Fullish and tailing on middle. Rahim drives it to mid on.
Sliding on middle and spinning away. Ali nudges it to mid-wicket for a single.

This is full and on middle. Rahim sweeps it hard and straight to the fielder at short leg. Sarel Erwee gets hit on the body and Rahim rushes quickly to check him out. Erwee gestures it hits him on top of his arm before the helmet. He looks fine though.
Full and on middle. blocked out on the front foot.
Another solid front foot defense from Mushfiqur Rahim.
Angles it full and on middle. Rahim gets low and defends it back to Maharaj.
Touch short but quicker and angling around off. Rahim on the back foot, blocks it out.
A length ball, outside off. Ali shoulders arms to it.
A length ball, slanting outside off and shaping away a touch. Ali leans to defend but does so inside the line.
Tad fuller and on off. Ali dead bats it.
Outside off. Left alone. Good take by the keeper as the ball was swirling in late.
A length ball, outside off. Ali has a feel for it but pulls out his bat on time.
Too full and straight on middle, flicked straight to mid-wicket.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Shortish delivery again, turning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Sharp spin there! Tad fuller, spinning away sharply, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim offers no shot to that.
Flatter ball, around middle and leg, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it to mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, around the pads, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it towards square leg.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim works it away wide of mid-wicket for a single. He retains the strike!
On a length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Another length delivery, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller delivery, angling in, around middle and off, at 127 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid off.
Pitches it up again, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim presses forward and blocks it out.
Full in length, outside off, at 124 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
On a length now, outside off, at 125 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it to towards mid off once again.
Fuller delivery, darting it on the pads, at 84 kph. Yasir Ali defends it towards short leg.
Shorter delivery, spinning away, outside off. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover for a brace.
Fuller delivery, around middle and leg. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Yasir Ali presses forward and blocks it out.

An absolute peach of a delivery! This one lands on a fuller length, around middle and spins away sharply outside off. Yasir Ali hangs back and looks to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Pitches it up, around middle. Yasir Ali defends it out.
Back of a length, shaping away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it past point for a single.
On a length, around middle. Yasir Ali defends it out.
Angling in around middle and leg, fuller ball. Yasir Ali flicks it past square leg. Ryan Rickelton chases it and keeps it down to one run.
Good-length delivery, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim defends this but the ball goes off the outer half of the bat towards gully. Single taken!
On a length, around middle. Yasir Ali defends it out.
Shorter ball, around middle. Yasir Ali swivels and pulls it gently towards fine leg. Two taken!
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim leans to defend this but the ball goes off the shoulder of the bat lobs up and lands safely away from silly point.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid on.
Shorter ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it past point for a single.

A huge shout for LBW, but no given! Fuller delivery, this one lands around the leg pole, and turns away around middle. Yasir Ali hangs back and looks to defend this but he misses and gets rapped his pads. South Africa opts for a review! No bat involved there and Ball Tracking shows it was pitching outside leg. South Africa have no reviews left now!
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Yasir Ali presses forward and blocks it out.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! Finally, Keshav Maharaj has been rewarded! He has been bowling well! Bangladesh loses their sixth wicket. A fuller ball, tosses it up, this one lands around middle and straightens. Yasir Ali tries to play against the turn as he looks to flick this on the leg side, but he manages to get a leading edge back to the bowler. Keshav Maharaj gets low, and takes the catch. He fumbled a bit and almost dropped it but made sure to stick both his arm together and hold onto it.
Howout: c & b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Outside off, on a length. Rahim has a poke at it but the ball just nips away off the deck.
Well outside off. Left alone.
A length ball from wide of the crease and angling around off. Rahim steps across and shoulders arms to it.
Length ball, outside off and moving more away. Rahim leaves it alone.
Mulder keeps bowling it outside off and Rahim is not tempted to chase these ones.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Hasan gets low to block it.
A bit quicker at 88 kph, around middle. Kept out.
Tossed up, on off. Hasan leans to defend it but gets a thick outside edge past gully for a single.
Full and on off. Rahim steps forward and pushes it aerially and to mid off.
Flatter and on middle. Rahim gets low to sweep and but gets a leading edge to deep square leg who collects it on a bounce.
Shorter and angling outside off. No turn there and Hasan makes an easy leave.
Length and outside off. Rahim shoulders arms to it.
Length ball, outside off. Rahim guides it through point for a single.
This is full and on middle. Hasan defends under his eyes but slices it to point.
Full and swinging outside off. Hasan offers no shot.
A bouncer, on middle, steep bounce as well. Hasan sits under it. The keeper takes it at a good height.
Full, too straight on the pads. Hasan flicks it square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Tossed up, on middle. Kept out.
Down the leg side. Rahim tucks it to square leg and thinks of a single, not taken in the end.

This one lands on off and spins away sharply. The length was a driving length and makes Rahim prod forward for a push but he misses. A stumping appeal but the square umpire takes his time before sending it upstairs. UltraEdge shows no bat there. The replay shows the back foot was grounded all along.
Tossed up, on middle. Rahim dead bats it on the leg side.
Slightly full and on off. Rahim reaches to the ball and blocks it.
Flatter and this one skids through. Rahim hangs back and defends it towards silly point.
Length ball, slanting on middle. Hasan hangs back and blocks it.
A length ball, on off. Hasan defends with soft hands and to squre leg for a single.
Fuller and on middle. Rahim works it to square leg for a single.
Short in length and angling down. Hasan lets it through.
Length and outside off, tapped to point for no run.
Length ball, outside off. Hasan plays it on the back foot and to point.
Fuller delivery, around middle Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it to the fielder at square leg.
Tosses it up, full again, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Pitches it up, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim works it away towards mid on.
Loopy delivery, full, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim presses forward and defends it out.
Flighted delivery, around middle, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Pitched up delivery again, fuller ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length, around middle. Mehidy Hasan stays in his crease and blocks it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan defends it out off the back foot.
FOUR! Pulled away! Shorter ball, around middle. Mehidy Hasan swivels and pulls it towards square leg for a boundary.
Length delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan pushes it toward cover for a single.
Shorter ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards gully.
Shorter ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it towards backward point for a single.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim presses forward and defends it out.
Tosses it up, fuller in length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim keeps it out.
Shorter ball now, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it towards point.
Tad quicker now, around middle, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Down leg, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it towards fine leg for a single.
FOUR! Mushfiqur Rahim brings up his fifty in style! A fuller length delivery, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
A huge shout for LBW, but not given! A shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back looks to defend this but he misses and gets rapped on the pads. That was probably too high!

OUT! TIMBER! Oh, dear! Mushfiqur Rahim has given his wicket away here! An unnecessary shot! Fuller delivery, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and tries to reverse-sweep this, but he misses. The ball deflects off his pads and goes on to hit the stumps. Bangladesh are now 7 down! Simon Harmer grabs his first wicket of the match.
Howout: b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Fuller ball, turning away, around off. Taijul Islam looks to block this, but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Turn and bounce again! Fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Taijul Islam once again gets beaten on the outside edge.
Shorter ball, around off. Taijul Islam defends it out.
Fuller delivery, tosses it up, around middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out solidy.
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Mehidy Hasan lunges forward and blocks it out.
Shortish delivery, around middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out off the back foot.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, spinning away. Mehidy Hasan leans to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Flighted delivery, full, around off. Mehidy Hasan defends it out.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around middle. Mehidy Hasan leans and defends it with the inner half of his bat. That will be Lunch on Day 3!
A fuller ball, on middle, pushed back to Harmer.
A flighted, full ball, drifting around middle. Islam blocks it on the surface.
Floated this time, around off. Islam drives it to mid off.
Full again from around the wicket, around off. Kept out.
Pitched up, on off. Islam prods and defends it on the off side.
Touch short and outside off. Islam cuts it late and past point for three runs. Good running.
Tossed up, on middle. Islam looks to heave but it goes off the inner half of the bat and well wide of deep square leg. A single.
A rank long hop, outside off. Hasan cuts it but straight to the point fielder.
Full and on off. Hasan gets low to defend but mistimes it and takes a single as it rolls to mid-wicket.

An appeal for a catch but not given! A flighted ball, on middle. Islam prods to defend but misses and gets hit on the pads. The ball lobs to first slip who takes it but there was no insdie edge there.
On middle. Blocked out.
Fullish and on middle. Islam swings his bat and looks to go big but miscues it to long on where the ball drops safe. A single.

OUT! TAKEN! Taijul Islam tried to stay aggressive but failed to middle any ball and this time he holes one out. Tossed up, full and around off, spinning away. Islam swings across and looks to go over mid-wicket but it takes the top edge and lobs towards mid off where Lizaad Williams takes a sharp catch.
Howout: c Lizaad Williams b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Shorter, outside off and this one spins back in sharply. Hasan is surprised by the spin but does well to defend it out.
Flatter and across, outside off. Hasan blocks it.
Fuller and down the leg side. Hasan misses his flick. An appeal follows but the umpire is not intrested.
Full and on middle. Hasan sweeps it but straight to short leg.
On middle, swept to square leg for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Hasan blocks it out.
Flighted, outside off. Hasan prods but goes back and cuts this to point.
Shorter and outside off. Hasan cuts it again to point.
Floated and on off. Hasan keeps it out on the off side.

OUT! TAKEN! This might have been the plan from Bangladesh to go out and look for biggies but failed to connect it! This is full and around off. Mehidy Hasan goes for the slog-sweep but fails to get the required distance. Duanne Olivier at deep square leg takes a good catch.
Howout: c Duanne Olivier b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: tossed up, on off. Ahmed defends it out.
A slider and around off, fuller and this is pushed back to the bowler.

OUT! TAKEN! That is the end of Bangladesh! Harmer gives flight to this one, around off. Hossain slog-sweeps it to deep mid-wicket where Lizaad Williams slightly misjudged the flight of the ball but did really well to take it over his head in the end. Bangladesh still trail by 236 runs.
Howout: c Lizaad Williams b Simon Harmer

Commentary: A huge appeal for LBW, but not given! A fuller ball, this one lands around leg and nips away towards off. Sarel Erwee looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his back pad. They decide not to go for the review! That was probably pitching outside leg.
Ouch! A shorter ball, outside off. Sarel Erwee cuts it towards point. Mehidy Hasan there had no idea where the ball was, and the ball goes on to hit him on the chest. He seems in a lot of pain there!
Outside off, shaping away, on a length. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
Length delivery, around middle. Sarel Erwee defends it out.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Sarel Erwee! A fuller ball, around middle and leg. Sarel Erwee flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary. South Africa and Sarel Erwee are up and running!

FOUR BYES! Down the leg side, length delivery. Sarel Erwee misses his flick, the keeper fails to grab it as well. The ball rolls towards fine leg for aboundary. Not the ideal start for Bangladesh. 8 runs off the first over!
Khaled Ahmed begins with a fuller ball, around middle. Dean Elgar pushes it towards mid off and takes a single. Dean Elgar gets off the mark!
On a length, shaping away, outside off. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off, at 133 clicks. Sarel Erwee blocks it out solidly.
Fuller delivery now, outside off, at 131 clicks. Sarel Erwee drives and finds the fielder at cover.
Well bowled! A tight leave by Sarel Erwee! On a length, nipping back in sharply, around the fourth stump line. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
Fullish delivery, around middle, at 134 clicks. Sarel Erwee defends it out.
Angling in, on a length, darting it on the pads, at 140 clicks. Dean Elgar tucks it towards square leg.
Fuller ball now, around middle and leg, swinging in. Dean Elgar flicks it past mid-wicket for a brace.
On a length, outside off. Dean Elgar leaves it alone.
Beaten! Fuller ball, outside off, hint of away movement there. Dean Elgar leans to drive this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! An overpitched delivery, around middle. Dean Elgar shows the full face of the bat and drives it straight down the ground for a boundary.
Fuller ball, around middle. Dean Elgar pushes it to mid on.
On a length, outside off. Sarel Erwee blocks it towards point.
Another length delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee taps it toward cover-point.
Angling in, around middle and leg. Sarel Erwee flicks it towards square leg.
FOUR! Classy from Erwee! Fuller delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee lunges forward and caresses it past extra cover for a boundary.
Length delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee taps it towards point.
Pitched up delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Dean Elgar works it away towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Fullish delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee pushes it towards point for a single.
Shorter ball, turning in, around middle. Dean Elgar flicks it towards square leg.

Tough chance goes down! A shorter ball, spinning in, around middle and leg. Dean Elgar flicks it towards short leg. The fielder there gets his hand to it but fails to hold on to it. Never easy to take those catches!
FOUR! Perfectly timed shot! Fuller ball, spinning in, around middle. Dean Elgar uses his wrists and flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Dean Elgar works it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Fuller and angling on middle. Erwee drives it through mid on for a boundary.
This is on a length and outside off. Erwee blocks it on the off side.
On the hips, flicked to mid-wicket for a single.
Full and way outside off. Elgar drives it past point for one more.
A length ball, on middle. Erwee tucks it to mid-wicket. Elgar was off for a single but gets a huge shout of 'NO' from the other side.
Straight, fuller and on middle. Erwee turns it to deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
tossed up, full and outside off. Elgar punches it through covers, wide of the fielder and gets a couple of runs.
Flatter and outside off. Left alone.
Outside off again, Dean knocks it to covers.
pitched up, on middle, driven back to the bowler.
tossed up, angling on full and curving away. Elgar leans to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
SIX! Bang! Fuller and outside off. Elgar drags it and hammers it all the way over mid-wicket for a biggie.
FOUR! South Africa are scoring at a quick rate! Full and around middle. Erwee reverse sweeps it through point for a boundary.
loopy ball, on off. Erwee hangs back and blocks it on the leg side.
On middle. Erwee reverse sweeps it to short third man for a single.
Flatter and around off. Elgar covers his stumps and keeps it out on the leg side.
Full and on off, eased down to long on for a single.
Full and outside off. Sarel guides it to point for a single.
Too full and on middle, slower through the air. Erwee blocks it.
Shorter and outside off. Erwee square cuts it behind square and beats the point fielder for a couple of runs.
Around off, pushed to mid off.
Touch short and outside off. Erwee slaps it to the fielder at point.
This one angles around off and spins away, on the shorter side. Left alone.
Flatter and on off, tucked to mid-wicket.
Full and on off. Elgar skips down and drills it to long on for a single.
Too full and on middle. Erwee flicks it to deep mid-wicket. Long on comes across and does well to save a single. Three runs taken.
Tossed up, on middle. Blocked out.
Flighted ball, full and spinning on middle. Elgar plays with the turn to square leg for a single.
Fullish and on middle, Erwee keeps it out.
Length ball, on off. Erwee rocks back, covers his stumps and blocks it out on the deck.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Dean Elgar leans and defends it out.
Shorter delivery, spinning away, outside off. Dean Elgar cuts it towards point for a single.
Outside again, short in length. Sarel Erwee pushes it towards cover and takes a single.
Quicker now, around middle, fuller ball. Dean Elgar blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, around middle. Dean Elgar knocks it down to long on for a single.
Shortish delivery, spinning away, outside off. Sarel Erwee manages to get an outside edge towards backward point for a single.
Around middle, fuller ball. Sarel Erwee taps it to square leg.
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Sarel Erwee gets down on his knee and reverse-sweeps it past point for a single.

OUT! TIMBER! Taijul Islam strikes and draws first blood! Elgar's over-aggressive approach has cost him his wicket here! A fuller ball, quicker, this one pitches around leg and turns in. Dean Elgar gets down on his knee and goes for the reverse-sweep but he misses. The ball goes on to hit the leg pole. Dean Elgar is not happy with himself!
Howout: b Taijul Islam

Commentary: Quicker ball, an arm ball on this occasion, around middle. Keegan Petersen looks to defend this but gets an inside edge to square leg.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Keegan Petersen pushes it past cover. Three taken!
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Sarel Erwee pushes it with the inner half of his bat towards square leg for a couple of runs.
Fuller ball, around middle. Keegan Petersen defends it out solidly.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg. Keegan Petersen pushes it off the back foot towards mid-wicket.
Fuller delivery, down the leg side. Keegan Petersen leaves it alone.
Fuller ball, around middle and off. Keegan Petersen steps down and eases it towards mid off.
Fuller and on off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, around off. Petersen defends it on the off side.
Fuller and on middle, Erwee eases it to the left of the bowler.
Tossed up, spinning back on middle. Erwee prods to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Touch short and on middle. Erwee hangs back and tucks it to square leg.
Sharp spin there! Flatter and down the leg side. Erwee misses his flick. A  stifled appeal follows but there was no bat there.
On middle. Blocked out.
This is full and on middle. Erwee looks to heave but gets an inside edge to square leg.

Shorter ball, wide off. Keegan Petersen hangs back and tries to cut this away, but the misses. The keeper collects the ball and whips the bails off. The third umpire checks for stumping. The replay shows that Keegan Petersen's back foot was just touching the ground while the bails were off. Not out it is! That was touch and go for the umpire.
FOUR! Beautifully played! Slower through the air, full, outside off. Keegan Petersen leans and drives it past cover for a boundary.
Fuller ball, around middle. Keegan Petersen knocks it down to long on for a single.
FOUR! A gift to Sarel Erwee! A low full toss, on the pads. Sarel Erwee flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Sarel Erwee leans and defends it out.
Tosses it up again, full, outside off. Sarel Erwee drives it towards deep cover for a single. He retains the strike!
Too full and floated, around off. Blocked back to the bowler.
On middle, eased down to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Petersen leans and keeps it out on the off side.
This is quicker, on a length and around off, steep bounce as well. Petersen does well to defend it out.
Length and on middle. Defended out.
Touch short and around off. Petersen wrists it through mid-wicket for a brace.
Floated ball, full and on off. Erwee carves it to point.
Too full and darted on leg. Erwee whacks it to deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Gives flight to this one, around off. Pushed to covers.
An arm ball, angling on middle. Defended out on the off side.
Very full and on middle. Sarel dead bats it.
Another solid block from Erwee to end the over.
Full and outside off, spinning away. Petersen waits and guides it to point.
FOUR! Sees a short ball, on middle. Petersen clears his front leg and pulls it to mid-wicket for a boundary.
Full ball, angling on middle. Petersen defends on the front foot.
Flatter and around off. Petersen rocks back and punches it straight to the cover fielder. It hits silly point actually.
Overpitched and outside off. Petersen drives it and the fielder at short cover dives to his right and makes a good stop.
Short and outside off. Petersen shoulders arms to it.
Floated, full and outside off, driven straight to cover.
Angles it on middle. Erwee on the front foot, defends it.
Flighted ball, tailing on middle. Erwee keeps it out.
Tossed up, on off. Erwee blocks it on the off side.
Goes wide of the crease and angles it on middle, pushed to mid on.
A slider and this one holds its line, around off. Erwee gets his bat down and defends it out.
A low full toss, angling on pads, flicked to mid-wicket.
Beauty! Need much more of this! tossed up, full and landing on off, this one spins away sharply. Petersen leans to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Too full and on middle. Petersen blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! A huge appeal for LBW and up goes the finger! Petersen has a chat with Erwee and takes the review. UltraEdge shows no bat involved. Ball Tracking shows umpire's call on wickets hitting and the on-field decision stays. Coming onto the ball - An arm ball, sliding on middle and this one does not spin much, it goes on with the arm. Petersen leans to defend but gets beaten on the inside edge and gets hit on the pads. An appeal and up goes the finger. The replay shows the ball goes onto clip the bails of leg stumps and that will also be Tea on Day 3.
Howout: lbw b Taijul Islam

Commentary: Fuller and around middle, it is pushed to mid on.
On a length and around off. Bavuma hangs back and punches off the back foot to covers.
Angling in around off, fuller in length. Sarel Erwee leans and taps it towards cover and takes a single.
FOUR! Temba Bavuma gets off the mark in style! A fuller ball from over the wicket, outside off. Temba Bavuma presses forward and drives it beautifully past cover for a boundary.
On a length, outside off. Temba Bavuma pushes it off the back foot towards cover-point for a single.

OUT! Khaled Ahmed comes into the attack and strikes straightaway! Perfect field placement by Mominul Haque and Sarel Erwee falls into the trap! A length ball, around middle. Sarel Erwee chips it straight to the man at short mid on. Mominul Haque there grabs it safely. South Africa lose their third wicket.
Howout: c Mominul Haque b Khaled Ahmed

Commentary: On a length, around middle and leg. Ryan Rickelton flicks it past mid-wicket for a single. He gets off the mark!
Good-length delivery, outside off. Temba Bavuma defends it back to the bowler.
Fuller ball, around off. Ryan Rickelton pushes it wide of cover for a single.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Temba Bavuma presses forward and defends it out.
Pitches it up again, outside off, spinning away. Temba Bavuma pushes it towards cover.
Loopy delivery, fuller in length, around middle. Temba Bavuma blocks it out solidly.
Shorter delivery, around middle. Temba Bavuma works it away past mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted delivery, full, around middle and off. Ryan Rickelton defends it out.
Angling in on the pads, on a length. Temba Bavuma flicks it past mid-wicket. The ball will not race away to the boundary, but the batters pick up three runs.
Good-length delivery, tailing back in around middle, at 134 clicks. Ryan Rickelton defends it out.
Fuller ball, outside off. Ryan Rickelton leans and drives it past the diving fielder at cover. Three runs taken!
On a length, around middle. Temba Bavuma flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Temba Bavuma shows the full face of the bat and drives it straight to the fielder at mid on.
Pitches it up, on middle. Temba Bavuma blocks it out solidly.
Tosses it up, full in length, around middle. Ryan Rickelton pushes it wide of mid on. Ebadot Hossain there, runs and dives to his right and makes a good stop. Single taken!
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Temba Bavuma leans and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, down the leg side this time. Temba Bavuma sweeps it towards deep square leg and takes a single.
Fuller ball, around middle. Ryan Rickelton defends it out.
FOUR! Nicely done! Pitches it up again, loopy delivery, outside off. Ryan Rickelton leans and drives it past the mid off for a boundary.
Slower through the air, full, around middle and leg. Ryan Rickelton clips it towards mid on.
Angling in, on a length, around middle. Temba Bavuma blocks it out off the back foot.
Another length delivery, outside off. Temba Bavuma blocks it out.
Angling in, fuller ball, around middle and leg. Temba Bavuma flicks it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Shorter ball, around middle. Temba Bavuma ducks underneath it.
Fuller delivery, around middle and leg. Temba Bavuma pushes it towards mid on.
Khaled Ahmed drops it short this time, around middle. Temba Bavuma pulls it to the fielder at fine leg.
Flatter and outside off. Bavuma prods to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fuller and on off, pushed to mid off for a single.
Tossed up, on middle, this is hit to mid on for a run.
Around off. Blocked out.
A loopy ball, outside off. Bavuma knocks it to the left of point for a quick single.
Full and on off. Rickelton looks to push but hits off the inner half of the bat to mid on.

Leg bye! A huge shout for LBW but nothing given! A length ball, around middle, it lands and nips back in. Bavuma looks to work it away on the leg side but misses and gets hit on the pads. Might be missing leg. A leg bye taken as well.
Length ball, from around the wicket and on middle. Rickelton blocks it out.
Short in length and around off. Rickelton pulls it to long leg for a single. Was in the air for a while but well short of the fielder.
Length and around off. Bavuma defends with soft hands and gets an outside edge, to the keeper who collects it in front of him.
This is down the leg side. Bavuma misses his flick.

On a length and around off, it nips away a touch. Bavuma looks to defend but inside edges it to point for a quick single. Ahmed was appealing for LBW and Bavuma was charging across for a quick single. Bavuma's helmet hits Ahmed's left arm and he looks a bit in pain.
FOUR! Good shot! Full and outside off. Bavuma drags it and sweeps it well to mid-wicket for a boundary.
Around off. Bavuma paddles it behind square on the leg side.
Tossed up, on middle. Rickelton leans to flick but gets an inside edge onto the pads. The ball lobs to the left of short leg and drops safely.
A fuller ball, around middle and leg. Ryan Rickelton gets down to sweep, but the ball goes off his glove and over the keeper's head. Yasir Ali from slip fails to get there on time.
Full and on middle. Rickelton presses forward and defends it out.
On middle, this is hit to mid-wicket.
Full ball, around off. Bavuma drives it firmly but straight to mid off.
Length ball, on middle. Bavuma lunges and defends it near to his pads.
Touch fuller and on off. Bavuma stays back and keeps it out on the off side.
Around off. shorter ball. Bavuma ducks under it.
Fullish and on off. Bavuma jams it out to cover.
On a length and around off. Bavuma taps it in front of covers and takes off for a quick single.
Tossed up, outside off, driven to mid off.
This one keeps coming with the angle, around off. Bavuma defends on the front foot.
Touch short and quicker, on middle. Bavuma blocks it on the leg side.
Flatter and outside off. Bavuma pushes it to point.
Darted on the pads, flicked to square leg for a single.

OUT! CAUGHT!  Taijul Islam strikes again! He is putting on a good show, personally. A loopy ball, full and on middle. Ryan Rickelton comes down the track and looks to push it straight but the ball goes off the inner half and goes flat to short mid on where Mominul Haque again takes a good low catch.
Howout: c Mominul Haque b Taijul Islam

Commentary: Angling in on a length, around middle and leg. Temba Bavuma tucks it towards deep square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle. Kyle Verreynne pushes it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
On a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne taps it towards point.
Fuller ball now, around middle. Kyle Verreynne pushes it back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it towards third man for a brace. He gets off the mark with that!
Khaled Ahmed drops it short now, outside off. Kyle Verreynne pulls it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Pitches it up, loopy delivery, around middle. Temba Bavuma gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards fine leg for a couple of runs.
Fuller ball, on middle. Temba Bavuma presses forward and defends it out.
Fuller delivery, outside off. Temba Bavuma leans forward to defend this, but the ball goes off the inside edge just away from the leg pole.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Temba Bavuma gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
FOUR! Shorter ball, width on offer this time. Kyle Verreynne slashes it past cover-point for a boundary.
Fuller ball, around middle. Kyle Verreynne flicks it past mid-wicket for a brace.
Shorter ball, outside off. Temba Bavuma punches it off towards deep cover for a brace.

Leg bye! A huge shout for LBW, but not given! That was probably too high! A length ball, nipping back in, around middle and leg. Temba Bavuma misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads. The ball rolls towards point and they take a leg bye.
Khaled Ahmed drops it short now, around middle. Kyle Verreynne pulls it towards deep square leg for a couple of runs.
On a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it towards cover.
Beaten! On a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays in his crease and looks to cut this away, but he misses.
Another length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne dabs it towards third man and rotates the strike.
FOUR! Kyle Verreynne shows some aggression! Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Kyle Verreynne gets down on his knee and sweeps it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
EDGED AND FOUR! Touch shorter now, outside off. Kyle Verreynne rocks back and looks to cut this, but the ball goes off the outside edge over the first slip fielder towards third man for a boundary.

JAFFA! What a peach by Taijul Islam! Slower through the air, full, spinning away outside off. Kyle Verreynne leans to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge and the ball goes just over the off pole.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Kyle Verreynne pushes it past cover for a single.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Temba Bavuma sweeps it uppishly over mid-wicket for a single.
Shorter ball, firing it on the thigh pads. Kyle Verreynne misses his flick. The ball deflects off his thigh pad and goes towards short leg.
Marginally short now, around middle. Temba Bavuma works it away towards square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne dabs it towards backward point for a single.
Another length ball, outside off. Temba Bavuma pushes it off the back foot towards deep point for a single. 150 up for South Africa!
Back of a length, outside off, at around 140 clicks. Kyle Verreynne defends it towards cover-point.
Length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne dabs it towards point.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Shorter ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne looks to slash this away, but the ball goes off the top edge towards the vacant third man region for a boundary.
Tossed up, full from over the wicket and on middle. Bavuma tucks it to square leg.
Full again. Bavuma flicks it to mid-wicket where Shanto makes a good stop to his right.
Tossed up, flighted and on middle. Bavuma nudges it to short mid-wicket.

OUT! LBW! An appeal for LBW and up goes the finger. Bavuma takes the review quickly. UltraEdge shows no bat while Ball Tracking shows three reds. This is very full and around middle and off, spinning in. Bavuma gets on his knee and looks to slog-sweep it but misses and the ball sneaks through and hits him on his back thigh.The replay shows the ball goes onto hit the leg stump. Bavuma walks back with a review with him.
Howout: lbw b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Fuller and on off. Mulder prods and defends.
Flatter and outside off. Left alone.
Fuller ball, outside off, nips away. Verreynne is not holding back as he swings hard but fails to connect.
FOUR! Nicely played! Short in length and outside off. Verreynne gets on his toes and punches it in the gap, to point for a boundary.
Full and on off, driven to deep cover for a single.
Tad full and on middle, it is hit to mid on.
Length and outside off. Mulder punches it straight to the cover fielder.
This is on a length and outside off at 140kph. Mulder has a feel for it as he flashes his bat but misses.
Tossed up, full and on middle, swept to deep square leg for a single.
Fullish and on off, slower ball. Mulder reverse sweeps it through point for a single.
On middle, flicked to square leg for a single.
Floated and on middle. Mulder skips down only to dead bats it.
FOUR! Flighted ball, on off. Mulder comes down the track and lofts it nicely over mid off for one bounce four. South Africa now lead by 402 runs.
Full and on middle, driven through mid on for a single.
Full ball, outside off. Mulder shoulders arms to it.
A length ball, tailing on the pads. Mulder misses his pull and gets hit on the pads. It rolls to fine leg for a leg bye.

This is short and down the leg side. Kyle Verreynne tries to ride the bounce and looks to pull but misses. The keeper is interested and asks Haque to take it upstairs. UltraEdge shows nothing on it and the review was more of an ambitious one. Not out it is.

FOUR! On the hips, Kyle Verreynne whacks it between, deep square leg and fine leg. Hasan at square leg, runs back, slides and flicks it back but his legs touches the ropes and the umpire signals a boundary after having a good look at it.
Short ball and on middle. Verreynne pulls it to deep mid-wicket and the fielder there dives to his right and stops it. Two runs taken.
On middle, nudged to mid-wicket for a single.
Leg bye! A fuller ball, spinning on the pads. Verreynne misses his flick and gets hit on the pads. The ball lobs past leg slip for a leg bye.
Darted on the pads. Mulder whips it to short leg and he does really well to stop the ball.
On middle. Blocked out.
Full and around off. Mulder keeps it out.

OUT! TIMBER! The ball hits the stumps and Dean Elgar from the balcony calls both the batters back. Declaration from South Africa and they lead by 412 runs. A floated, length ball, around off, it spins back in slightly. Wiaan Mulder leans and looks to defend the wrong line but misses and gets beaten on the outside edge. The ball goes onto rattle the off stump.
Howout: b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Starts with a full ball, outside off. Iqbal steps across and blocks it out.
This is full and angling on middle. Iqbal leans to block it but gets an inside edge and o the right of leg slip. A single taken and Bangladesh are off in the chase.

OUT! EDGED AND GONE! Keshav Maharaj loves to bowl in the fourth innings! Tossed up, on a length and around off, this one skids through and does not turn much. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and looks to defend but gets an outside edge to the keeper who gets a glove on it and the ball deflects to gully where Wiaan Mulder takes it. Mahmudul Hasan Joy nicked it but still was thinking of a review. That will be a pair for Mahmudul Hasan Joy!
Howout: c Wiaan Mulder b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: FOUR! Ohh, almost another wicket! Full ball, and outside off. Shanto looks to drive but gets an inside edge past the leg stump and to fine leg for a boundary.
Around off. Blocked out.
Slightly short and on middle. Shanto tucks it to square leg for a single.
On middle, fuller and Shanto comes forward to block it.
Tossed up, on off. Shanto keeps it out on the off side.
Flatter and outside off, Shanto gets his pad in the line.
Two byes! This one lands on off and spins away sharply with some serious bounce. The keeper fails to collect it and two runs are taken.
On middle. Blocked out.
Darted on the pads. Shanto flicks it in front of square on the leg side for a couple.
Flatter, on a length and on middle. Iqbal rocks back and wrists it to deep square leg for a single.

OUT! LBW! Maharaj with an absolute beauty of a delivery! On a length and outside off, it lands and spins back in sharply. Shanto steps across and looks to defend but gets beaten by the turn there. He gets hit on the pads and a sharp appeal follows. The umpire raises his finger and South Africa celebrate but Shanto takes the review. He thinks that might go onto miss the leg stump but Ball Tracking shows it is the umpire's call on wickets hitting. Bangladesh are already in a lot of trouble and it is Keshav Maharaj who is making it difficult for them!
Howout: lbw b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Full and turning on middle. Haque flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
FOUR! Iqbal will not mess around, he will be aggressive as much as he can be! Tossed up, on middle. Iqbal slog-sweeps it behind square on the leg side for a boundary.

CHANCE! Full and outside off, again sharp turn there. Iqbal steps across to block it but gets an inside edge and the ball balloons behind short leg and in front of square leg. Both run towards the ball and both leave it for each other. Okay, there was no bat there.
Outside off. Iqbal blocks it out.
This one lands on off and spins away sharply. Haque looks to defend on the front foot but misses.
Touch fuller and this time Haque blocks it out.
Full and on off. Haque drives it to covers.
A flighted ball, tailing on the pads. Haque keeps it out on the leg side.
Floated this time, outside off. Haque gets low and guides it to point.
On middle. Blocked out.
Too full and on middle. Iqbal prods and defends it to the leg side.
Maharaj keeps bowling outside off. Iqbal gets inside the line and blocks it out.
Around off, drilled down to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on off, spinning back sharply. Haque prods to defend but misses and the ball goes to the left of leg slip who catches it one handed. There was no bat on it.
Sharp turn again. Haque misses his defensive shot and gets hit on the pads.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
Fuller ball, outside off, spinning away. Tamim Iqbal leans to block this and but he gets beaten.
Loopy ball, outside off, fuller in length. Tamim Iqbal defends it out.
Shorter ball now, around off. Tamim Iqbal defends it out off the back foot.
Short again, outside off. Tamim Iqbal pushes it towards cover.
FOUR! Loopy delivery, full, outside off. Tamim Iqbal leans and drives it past cover for a boundary.
Full, around middle. Tamim Iqbal leans to flick this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards point.
Full, around middle and leg. Mominul Haque flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Pitches it up again, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it towards mid off.
Loopy ball, full, outside off. Mominul Haque guides it towards third man for a brace.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mominul Haque leans and defends it out.
Tosses it up, full again, around middle. Mominul Haque blocks it out off the front foot.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mominul Haque leans and drives it past cover for a couple of runs.
Spinning away, outside off, fuller ball. Tamim Iqbal pushes it towards deep cover for two runs!
Quicker, flatter, around middle, shorter ball. Tamim Iqbal defends it out off the back foot.
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Tamim Iqbal leans and defends it out.
Tosses it up again, fuller ball, around middle. Tamim Iqbal blocks it out.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Tamim Iqbal leans and defends it out towards the off side.
Fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Tamim Iqbal leaves it alone.
Pitches it up, around middle. Mominul Haque knocks it towards mid on.
Shorter ball, turning in, around middle. Mominul Haque tucks it to the fielder at square leg.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it to the fielder at cover.

A huge shout for LBW, but not given! A fuller ball, spinning in, around middle. Mominul Haque leans to defend this but he misses and gets rapped on his pads. The replay shows that the impact was outside.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mominul Haque leans and gets beaten on the outside edge!
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Mominul Haque pushes it towards square leg.

OUT! EDGED AND TAKEN! It's Simon Harmer who strikes this time! He gets rid of the dangerous Tamim Iqbal! Beautiful delivery by Simon Harmer! A loopy delivery, full, spinning away, outside off. Tamim Iqbal leans to defend this, but the ball goes off the shoulder of the bat due to some extra bounce and lobs up towards Wiaan Mulder at first slip, who pouches it safely. Bangladesh lose their third wicket. That will be Stumps on Day 3!
Howout: c Wiaan Mulder b Simon Harmer

Commentary: FOUR BYES! A fuller ball, turning in, down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim misses his flick and Kyle Verreynne fails to grab the ball as well. It races away towards fine leg for a boundary. Bangladesh are underway on Day4!

A huge shout for LBW, but not given! Turn and bounce once again! A fuller ball, around off, spinning in sharply. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back and looks to flick this but he misses and gets rapped on the pads. South Africa opts for a review. No bat involved there. Ball Tracking shows it was too high and that would have gone over the stumps. South Africa lose a review!
Sharp turn again! A fuller ball, spinning in sharply, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Loopy ball, full, turning in, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim leans to defend this but the ball goes off the shoulder of the bat over the leg slip fielder. Single taken!
Around the leg pole, fuller ball. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps and it hits the short leg fielder on his pads.
Full, loopy ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out. A late no ball called as well.
Full again, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid off.

OUT! EDGED AND TAKEN! Early success for South Africa! Keshav Maharaj strikes in his first over of the day. He gets his third wicket and Bangladesh are now 4 down! Lovely delivery by Maharaj. Tosses it up nicely, fuller ball, this one lands around middle and spins away. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to drive this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards first slip. Dean Elgar there takes a good catch to his left.
Howout: c Dean Elgar b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Fuller ball, outside off. Liton Das pushes it towards cover-point.
Fuller ball, drifting in, around middle. Liton Das pushes it towards mid on for a single.
Shorter ball, around middle. Mominul Haque blocks it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball, around off. Liton Das advances down the track and looks to heave this away, but he misses and gets hit on his pads.
Turn and bounce! Shorter ball, spinning in sharply. Liton Das backs away and does well to fend it away on the off side.
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Liton Das leans to block this, but the ball goes off the inside edge onto the pads and just away from the short leg fielder.
Shorter ball, around middle. Liton Das defends it out off the back foot.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Liton Das pushes it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Fuller ball, loopy delivery, around middle. Liton Das advances down the pitch and lifts it over the bowler's head for a boundary.

OUT! TAKEN! Another one goes down! Keshav Maharaj strikes once again! He is one wicket away from a five-wicket haul now. Loopy ball, full, around off. Mominul Haque gets down on his knee and looks to sweep this, but the ball goes off the top edge and lobs up towards mid-wicket. Ryan Rickelton there takes an easy catch. Bangladesh have lost half their side now.
Howout: c Ryan Rickelton b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: FOUR! Top shot! Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Liton Das makes room and punches it past cover for a boundary.
Tosses it up, full, on middle. Liton Das blocks it out.
Another flighted delivery, fuller ball, around middle. Liton Das defends it out solidly.
Shorter ball, around middle. Liton Das nudges it towards mid-wicket and scampers through to the other end. A better throw at the keeper's end and Yasir Ali could have been in trouble there!
Outside off, shorter ball. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover.
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Liton Das cuts it towards point.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Liton Das pushes it towards mid on.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Liton Das drives it towards long off for a single.
Spinning in, around the pads, fuller ball. Yasir Ali leaves it alone, the ball hit his pads and lobs up towards leg slip.
Fuller ball, another off break, on the pads. Yasir Ali gets back and looks to block this but he misses.

OUT! CAUGHT! Another one bites the dust! Bangladesh are falling apart here! Simon Harmer gets his second wicket now. A loopy ball, full, around middle. Yasir Ali gets down on his knee and slog sweeps this towards deep mid-wicket. Lizaad Williams is perfectly placed there, and he takes it easily.
Howout: c Lizaad Williams b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Tosses it up, full, around middle. Mehidy Hasan defends it towards silly point.
Another fuller ball, around middle and off. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.
Drifting in, around middle, fuller ball. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.
A huge appeal for LBW but not given! This one slides in and lands around leg. Hasan prods to defend but misses and gets hit on the pads. Might be angling down.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out watchfully.
On middle. Hasan mistimes his sweep towards square leg. All along the ground.
Fuller and on middle. Das leans and blocks it out.
Length ball, angling outside off. Das watchfully leaves it alone.
Flatter and around off. Das hangs back and tucks it to short leg.
Too full and on off. Das whips it past mid-wicket for a single.
A flighted ball, full and on middle. Hasan lunges and keeps it out.
This is touch short but with good amount of spin. Hasan goes back and looks to punch but gets cramped for the room.
Tossed up, on middle. Das drills it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Das is not letting the loose balls go away! This is short and outside off. Das rocks back and cuts it past point for a boundary.
Tossed up, angling on middle. Das defends on the front foot.
FOUR! Again short and way outside off. Das has enough time to go back and cuts off the back foot through point for a boundary.
Short again, outside off. Das works through covers for a couple of runs.
An arm ball, drifting on middle and leg. Das prods and keeps it out on the leg side.
Length ball, on off. Hasan sweeps it to deep square leg for a single.
Tossed up, on middle. Das is too early as he pushes this and almost gifts a catch but the ball falls short of mid on.
Darted on the pads. Das keeps it out.
On middle. Blocked out.
FOUR! Good shot! Das is showing good intent! Full and angling outside off. Das skips down and hammers it well over mid on for a boundary.
Flatter and around off and middle. Das stays inside his crease to watchfully block it.
A quicker ball, around middle. Hasan defends under his eyes.
Tossed up, on off. Hasan drags it from outside off and looks to sweep but gets a top edge to deep square leg. The batters will take a couple of runs.
This one lands on off and spins away sharply. Hasan prods to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
On middle. Blocked out.
Another solid defense from Mehidy Hasan.
Tosses it up, full, outside off, spinning away. Mehidy Hasan leans to block this he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Full and down the leg side, spinning more away. Das shoulders arms to it.
Tossed up, outside off Das works it through covers for a single.
Length and on middle. Hasan defends it out on the front foot.
FOUR! Well played! Floated and on middle. Hasan sweeps it, gets hit on the arm and the ball rolls away to the fine leg fence.
On middle, swept to long leg again for a couple of runs.
Flighted ball, angling around middle. Hasan leans and defends it.

OUT! STUMPED! There it is! Keshav Maharaj gets another five-wicket haul! What a series he has been having! He gets rid of Liton Das this time. Another peach of a delivery. A loopy ball, full, this one lands around the leg pole and spins away sharply. Liton Das advances down the pitch and looks to heave this over on the leg side, but he gets beaten due to the turn. Kyle Verreynne collects the ball and whips the bails off. The replay shows that Liton Das was way out of his crease. He has to walk back!
Howout: st Kyle Verreynne b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Fuller ball, around middle. Taijul Islam blocks it out.
Another fuller delivery, around middle and leg. Taijul Islam flicks it towards leg slip.
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Taijul Islam leans to and defends it out.
Loopy ball, around middle, fuller ball. Taijul Islam turns it towards short leg.
Outside off, fuller ball. Taijul Islam presses forward and defends it out.
Drifting in, around middle and leg. Mehidy Hasan flicks it towards leg slip.
SIX! BOOM! Great use of teh feet by Mehidy Hasan! A fuller ball, around middle. Mehidy Hasan dances down the pitch and tonks it over the bowler's head for a biggie!
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Mehidy Hasan pushes it past cover for a single.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Taijul Islam blocks it out.
Loopy ball, full again, around off. Taijul Islam defends it out solidly.
Slower through the air, fuller ball, around off. Taijul Islam defends it towards point.
FOUR! Nicely done! Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Mehidy Hasan pushes it off the back foot past cover-point for a boundary.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mehidy Hasan leans and defends it out.

OUT! Keshav Maharaj gets his sixth wicket now! He just cannot stop taking wickets! Another beauty by Keshav Maharaj! A loopy ball, full again, this one lands around middle and spins away. Mehidy Hasan leans to block this but the manages to get a slight outside edge back to the keeper. A huge appeal for caught behind, but the umpire says no. South Africa opts for a review! UltraEdge does show a spike and Mehidy Hasan walks back.
Howout: c Kyle Verreynne b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Khaled Ahmed leans to block this but he misses.
Full, loopy ball, around middle. Khaled Ahmed blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! 7 wickets in Durban and now 7 wickets in Port Elizabeth. Take a bow, Keshav Maharaj! This is also his 150th Test wicket! Another fuller delivery, this one comes in with the arm, around middle. Khaled Ahmed presses forward to block this but he misses and gets hit on his pads. A huge appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger. Khaled Ahmed does go up for the review! No bat involved there, confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracking shows three reds. Khaled Ahmed departs and South Africa are one wicket away.
Howout: lbw b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Tossed up, full and around off, it lands and spins away. Islam looks to defend but misses.
Same line, same length as the previous delivery. this one spins away sharply. Islam looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.

OUT! LBW! Unbelievable performance from the hosts. Floated ball, on a length and angling around middle. Islam prods to defend near his pads but misses and gets hit on the pads. A huge appeal for LBW and up goes the finger. Islam takes a review, more of an ambitious one. UltraEdge shows no bat while Ball Tracking shows three reds and South Africa win by 332 runs and seal the series as well.
Howout: lbw b Simon Harmer
